phrase: While inexperienced, this mercenary braved the journey to the Soltrium galaxy and seeks to prove their worth in battle.
translation: Čeprav neizkušen, se je ta plačanec pogumno odpravil v galaksijo Soltrium in želi dokazati svojo vrednost v bitki

phrase: This solo operative seeks nothing but victory when it comes to saving their race from destruction.
translation: Ta samostojni operativec si prizadeva le za zmago, ko želi rešiti svojo raso pred uničenjem

phrase: A deadly sniper at range and a swift killer up close, they are capable of holding their own in any encounter.
translation: So smrtonosni ostrostrelci na daljavo in hitri ubijalci od blizu, ki se lahko borijo v vsakem spopadu

phrase: This commander lost their arm during the Flare but continues to fight for the future of their race.
translation: Ta poveljnik je med izbruhom plamenice izgubil roko, vendar se še naprej bori za prihodnost svoje rase

phrase: Outlaws that roam the outskirts of the galaxy, attacking anyone that dares travel alone.

translation: Ta Agaman se je na frontah vztrajno boril, da bi dokazal, da je vreden vstopa v galaksijo Soltrium

phrase: This Agaman gave up everything to make the journey to the Soltrium galaxy.
translation: Ta Agaman se je odpovedal vsemu, da bi odpotoval v galaksijo Soltrium

translation: Agamanu so v poskusu, s katerim so želeli ustvariti neustavljivo mešanico mesa in stroja, vlili soltrium

phrase: Click the Play tab when you are ready

translation: Vsi igralci začnejo z enako naključno izbrano opremo

phrase: Maps you have subscribed to in the workshop will appear here. You may need to refresh multiple times after subscribing to a new map for the list to update fully.
translation: Tukaj se bodo prikazali zemljevidi, na katere ste se naročili v delavnici. Po naročilu na nov zemljevid boste morda morali večkrat osvežiti, da se seznam v celoti posodobi

phrase: This game mode is called Salvage. Two teams contest a canister that contains a valuable resource called Soltrium.
translation: Ta način igre se imenuje Reševanje. Dve ekipi se potegujeta za posodo, ki vsebuje dragoceno surovino, imenovano soltrium

phrase: The team with the most players near the canister will extract Soltrium and earn points for their team. This can be seen at the top of the screen.
translation: Ekipa, ki bo imela največ igralcev v bližini posode, bo pridobila soltrium in osvojila točke za svojo ekipo. To lahko vidite na vrhu zaslona

phrase: When a canister is depleted, a new one will spawn elsewhere. The first team to reach 500 points wins!
translation: Ko je posoda izpraznjena, se na drugem mestu pojavi nova. Zmaga ekipa, ki prva doseže 500 točk

phrase: Ammo Bonuses drop when a player dies. Pick them up to get extra ammo for your weapons and earn 2 points for your team.
translation: Bonusi za strelivo padejo, ko igralec umre. Če jih poberete, dobite dodatno strelivo za orožje in zaslužite 2 točki za svojo ekipo

phrase: This game mode is called Breakthrough. To win, your team must control all five zones.
translation: Ta način igre se imenuje Breakthrough. Za zmago mora vaša ekipa nadzorovati vseh pet območij

phrase: When a zone is captured by your team, it will be frozen for up to 20 seconds. While frozen the enemy cannot retake it, which gives your team the chance to push forward into the next zone.
translation: Ko vaša ekipa zavzame območje, bo zamrznjeno do 20 sekund. Ko je območje zamrznjeno, ga sovražnik ne more ponovno zavzeti, kar vaši ekipi omogoča, da se pomakne naprej v naslednje območje

phrase: Zones must be captured in order and cannot be back-capped.
translation: Območja je treba osvojiti po vrstnem redu in jih ni mogoče pokriti nazaj

phrase: This game mode is called Control Shift. There is one zone and the objective is to push that zone all the way back into enemy territory.
translation: Ta način igre se imenuje Control Shift. Na voljo je eno območje, cilj pa je to območje potisniti nazaj na sovražnikovo ozemlje

phrase: The zone will begin moving when one team has more players inside it than the other.
translation: Območje se začne premikati, ko ima ena ekipa v njem več igralcev kot druga

phrase: This game mode is called Escort. To win, your team must deliver 3 bombs.
translation: Ta način igre se imenuje Escort. Za zmago mora vaša ekipa dostaviti 3 bombe

phrase: Each team has a bomb that they must pick up from their side of the map and deliver to the enemy bomb site.
translation: Vsaka ekipa ima bombo, ki jo mora pobrati na svoji strani zemljevida in jo dostaviti na sovražnikovo mesto bombe

phrase: You can either escort your bomb carrier, or defend your bomb site from the enemy.
translation: Spremljate lahko svoj nosilec bomb ali pa branite svoje mesto za bombe pred sovražnikom

phrase: This game mode is called Capture the Flag. Each team has a flag that they must defend.
translation: Ta način igre se imenuje Ujemi zastavo. Vsaka ekipa ima zastavo, ki jo mora braniti

phrase: To win your team must steal the enemy flag and take it back to your base 3 times.
translation: Za zmago mora vaša ekipa ukrasti sovražnikovo zastavo in jo trikrat odnesti v svojo bazo

phrase: You can either infiltrate the enemy base, or defend your flag from the enemy.
translation: Lahko se infiltrirate v sovražnikovo bazo ali branite svojo zastavo pred sovražnikom

phrase: This game mode is called Gun Game. Each player starts with the same weapon and progresses to the next weapon after getting 2 kills.
translation: Ta način igre se imenuje Gun Game. Vsak igralec začne z istim orožjem in po dveh ubijanjih preide na naslednje orožje

phrase: The stage that each player is up to is shown at the top of the screen.
translation: Stopnja, do katere je prišel vsak igralec, je prikazana na vrhu zaslona

phrase: To win you must advance to Stage 11 and then kill an enemy with either your digger or your knife.
translation: Če želite zmagati, morate napredovati do 11. stopnje in nato z bagrom ali nožem ubiti sovražnika

phrase: When dying to fall damage or an enemy digger/knife, you will be sent back one stage.
translation: Ko umrete zaradi poškodb pri padcu ali sovražnikovega kopača/noža, boste poslani za eno stopnjo nazaj

phrase: This free-for-all game mode is called Head Hunter. To win, you must hold the most Soltrium when the timer runs out.
translation: Ta način igre "prosto za vse" se imenuje Lovec na glave. Če želite zmagati, morate imeti največ Soltrija, ko se izteče časomer

phrase: Each player starts with nothing and collects weapons and mods from around the map.
translation: Vsak igralec začne z ničemer in zbira orožje in modifikacije z vsega zemljevida

phrase: When a player dies, they will drop their weapons, half their Soltrium and half their mods.
translation: Ko igralec umre, izgubi orožje, polovico soltrija in polovico modov

phrase: Pick up Soltrium to win, but be careful as the player with the most Soltrium will be revealed to everyone.
translation: Za zmago zbirajte Soltrium, vendar bodite previdni, saj bo igralec z največ Soltrija razkrit vsem

phrase: This arena game mode is called Spire. To win, you must eliminate the enemy team 5 times.
translation: Ta način igre v areni se imenuje Spire. Če želite zmagati, morate petkrat izločiti sovražnikovo ekipo

phrase: Each player starts with nothing and must build into the sky to pick up weapons.
translation: Vsak igralec začne z ničlo in mora graditi v nebo, da bi zbral orožje

phrase: This arena game mode is called Static. To win, you must eliminate the enemy team 5 times.
translation: Ta način igre v areni se imenuje Statična. Če želite zmagati, morate petkrat izločiti sovražnikovo ekipo

phrase: Each player shares the same loadout, which is randomised each round.
translation: Vsak igralec ima enako opremo, ki se naključno določi v vsakem krogu
Spremenite strukturo in nadaljujte z delom

Select a weapon from the gun rack
translation: Izberite orožje s stojala za orožje

phrase: Shoot the targets and try different weapons. Press
translation: Streljajte na tarče in preizkusite različna orožja. Pritisnite

translation: v klepetu, da določite svojo točko drstenja

translation: Odstranitev podaljšanih časovnih okvirov orožja. Igralci so nepremagljivi

translation: Opomba - če zahtevate vstop v lobby, se krog začne znova

phrase: Show Enemies on the Zone Bar
Spend more time on the CPU producing higher quality world meshes, which reduces pressure on the GPU.
translation: Več časa porabi procesor za izdelavo kakovostnejših mrež sveta, kar zmanjša pritisk na grafični procesor

phrase: The game will automatically disable effects and lower postprocessing quality to keep FPS high. It may take up to one minute to determine optimal rendering settings.
translation: Igra bo samodejno onemogočila učinke in znižala kakovost naknadne obdelave, da bi ohranila visoko raven FPS. Določitev optimalnih nastavitev upodabljanja lahko traja do ene minute

phrase: Changes how often you receive player data from the server. Lower this value if you are on unstable or low-bandwidth internet.
translation: Spremeni pogostost prejemanja podatkov o igralcih iz strežnika. Če imate nestabilen internet ali internet z majhno pasovno širino, zmanjšajte to vrednost

phrase: Must keep enabled at all times
The size of the bottom-right minimap
The internal scale of the bottom-right minimap
The server name will not be displayed on the scoreboard and other player names and levels will be randomised for you.
translation: Ime strežnika ne bo prikazano na tabli z rezultati, imena drugih igralcev in ravni pa bodo naključno izbrani

translation: Določa, ali se izriše igralni HUD. Bližnjica:

translation: Nadzoruje, ali se prikažejo imena igralcev. Bližnjica:

phrase: Particles are produced when objects are hit or destroyed. Lowering this percentage will increase FPS
translation: Delci nastanejo, ko se predmeti zadenejo ali uničijo. Znižanje tega odstotka bo povečalo FPS

phrase: The map is divided into chunks of 32x32x32 blocks. Reducing this will increase FPS
translation: Zemljevid je razdeljen na dele po 32x32x32 blokov. Zmanjšanje tega števila bo povečalo FPS

phrase: The world is illuminated by sun lights, block lights and muzzle flashes from guns. Reducing the maximum amount of lights that can be rendered will increase FPS
translation: Svet je osvetljen s sončnimi lučmi, svetlobnimi bloki in bliskavicami iz pušk. Z zmanjšanjem največje količine luči, ki jih je mogoče upodobiti, se bo povečal FPS

phrase: Frames per Second (FPS) is the amount of times the game will update each second. Lowering this value will decrease CPU and GPU usage
translation: Število sličic na sekundo (FPS) je število posodobitev igre vsako sekundo. Znižanje te vrednosti bo zmanjšalo porabo procesorja in grafičnega procesorja

phrase: Screen Space Ambient Occlusion darkens the crevices between objects
translation: Zaslonski prostor Ambientna okluzija zatemni razpoke med predmeti

phrase: Bloom increases and blurs the brightness of emissive surfaces
translation: Bloom poveča in zamegli svetlost oddajnih površin

phrase: Crepuscular rays are shafts of lights that originate from a star
translation: Krepuskularni žarki so svetlobni snopi, ki izvirajo iz zvezde

phrase: Parts of the map will be darkened by the shadows cast from other objects
translation: Deli zemljevida bodo zatemnjeni zaradi senc, ki jih mečejo drugi predmeti

phrase: Controls whether players from casting shadows
translation: Nadzoruje, ali igralci ne mečejo senc

phrase: Controls whether Disruptors, C4, Scanners and Canisters cast shadows
translation: Določa, ali rušilci, C4, skenerji in kanistri mečejo sence

phrase: Controls whether leaf particles cast shadows
translation: Nadzoruje, ali delci listov mečejo sence

phrase: Controls whether falling structures cast shadows
translation: Določa, ali padajoče strukture mečejo sence

phrase: Multisampling smooths the edges of objects
The Bare Minimum rendering mode skips all postprocessing and renders objects directly to the screen. Disabling this may take some time
translation: Način upodabljanja Bare Minimum preskoči vso naknadno obdelavo in predmete upodablja neposredno na zaslon. Izklop tega načina lahko traja nekaj časa

phrase: With Bare Minimum enabled, this controls whether the region around 2X and 4X scopes is blurred or black
translation: Če je omogočena možnost Bare Minimum, ta nastavitev določa, ali je območje okoli 2X in 4X daljnogleda zamegljeno ali črno

phrase: Compressing textures will use less memory on the GPU but the game will take longer to start up
translation: Stiskanje tekstur bo porabilo manj pomnilnika v grafičnem procesorju, vendar se bo igra zaganjala dlje časa

phrase: Debug logging stores log files in the AppData/Roaming/Vercidium/log folder, which helps the developers fix bugs and crashes
translation: Pri beleženju odpravljanja napak se dnevniške datoteke shranjujejo v mapo AppData/Roaming/Vercidium/log, kar razvijalcem pomaga pri odpravljanju napak in okvar

phrase: Safe Mode prevents crashes from closing the game, but may slow the game down slightly
translation: Varni način preprečuje, da bi se igra zaradi okvare zaprla, vendar lahko igro nekoliko upočasni

phrase: Vertical sync matches the update rate of the game to the refresh rate of your monitor. Enabling this may fix screen tearing
translation: Navpična sinhronizacija usklajuje hitrost posodabljanja igre s hitrostjo osveževanja vašega monitorja. Če to omogočite, lahko odpravite trganje zaslona

phrase: Dynamic Exposure mimics the human eye by adjusting exposure based on the brightness of the scene
translation: Dinamična osvetlitev posnema človeško oko s prilagajanjem osvetlitve glede na svetlost prizora

phrase: Reducing the quality of shadows will increase FPS but cause close-up shadows to flicker
translation: Zmanjšanje kakovosti senc bo povečalo število FPS, vendar bodo sence od blizu utripale

phrase: Reducing the quality of lighting will increase FPS but pixelate lighting
translation: Zmanjšanje kakovosti osvetlitve bo povečalo število FPS, vendar bo osvetlitev postala bolj pikselska

phrase: Enabling this will remove parts of the rendering pipeline that are potentially slow on older hardware
translation: Če to omogočite, boste odstranili dele cevovoda za upodabljanje, ki so na starejši strojni opremi lahko počasni

phrase: Enable this if you are having trouble connecting to servers
translation: Če imate težave s povezovanjem s strežniki, to omogočite
